title: @danielhowell
body:
@danielhowell this is important ok.

hi, so mine own nameth is.  [dan].  Nice to meeteth thee.  And this is mine own first ‘prop'r’ video i guesseth.  Woo!  i cullionly, i’ve kind of at each moment did want to beest someone who is’t posts videos, but i guesseth i’ve nev'r very much hadst the confidence 'r the motivation.  sayeth the p'rson with tissue pap'r all ov'r his visage.  But, yond wast until some very much valorous cater-cousins i’ve madeth recently p'rsuad’d me to giveth t a did shoot.  And so i am! i soundeth nothing liketh this in real life by the way.  This laptop’s microphone maketh me soundeth liketh some tramp/polar beareth.  please taketh not t p'rsonally.  mine own videos shall belike beest a variety of things, from liketh dram skits, to vloggy videos 'r creative things.  I’m going to tryeth to maketh those folk int'resting and not all the same.  Yeah, i’m going to tryeth mine own most wondrous to not just beest liketh one of those people who is’t sits th’re liketh: “hi, so the present day kinda did suck. Uh, wenteth to college, and t wast rainin’. Yeah. This is kinda contrary, i knoweth not what to sayeth. yeah.  I’m belike gonna wend anon. ” but yeah, i’m gonna tryeth mine own most wondrous to at least attempteth to beest ent'rtaining. so yeah, if ’t be true thee couldst prithee click the yellow boxeth of infinite happiness.  Causeth i’m gonna starteth making videos quite anon, i’ve did get loads of ideas, and i’ll tryeth to posteth videos regularly . What has’t i done to mine own visage? bleurgh.  Side noteth: behold what i did wake up with.   i just- i just did wake up and yond wast on mine own armeth?! what the *beep* is yond!? its liketh some bloody p'rson’s cometh up with a square brand and just impal’d me in mine own catch but a wink.  Belike.  So yeah, if ’t be true thee’d liketh to subscribe then i shall loveth thee f'rev'r and i shall seeth thee anon! what the *beep* am i doing?

summary:
Have I saved these pictures or have these pictures saved me?
Thank you, @danielhowell, for saving me from embarassment and...
body:
Have I saved these pictures or have these pictures saved me?

Thank you, @danielhowell, for saving me from embarassment and carrying our conversation

And

Thank you, @amazingphil, for the best hug I’ve gotten in years. It’s true what they say, you don’t ever let go unless we do it first.

The show was spectacular and fun, I can’t even stop smiling after it ended.. plus Manila felt how you really worked hard to make it special for us Filipino audience.

Here’s hoping against hope you come back in the near future (vacation? Tour? Eat another box of curly tops? Your call.)
